OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772644279
OL,3,C#100m cycle lane labelled 'dangerous'
OL,4,Cafter girl, 13, injured on scooter
OL,6,FA 13-year-old girl has been seriously
OL,7,Finjured after falling off her scooter
OL,8,Fon one of the new cycle lanes in
OL,9,FBournemouth and Poole, raising fresh
OL,10,Fsafety concerns over the multi-million-
OL,11,Fpound transport scheme.
OL,13,FLaila was on her way to school when
OL,14,Fthe accident happened.
OL,16,FShe was treated in hospital and is now
OL,17,Frecovering at home. Her mother filmed
OL,18,Fthe surface of the cycle lane, which
OL,19,Fshe believes is dangerous, and has the
OL,20,Fsupport of her local MP.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
