OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772644279
OL,3,C#100m cycle lane labelled 'dangerous'
OL,4,Cafter girl, 13, injured on scooter
OL,6,FNeil Duncan-Jordan, has written to BCP
OL,7,FCouncil seeking reassurances that the
OL,8,Flanes are being installed safely.
OL,10,FThe MP for Poole said "a lot of people
OL,11,Fargue they're not well used, that
OL,12,Fthere's been money put into those
OL,13,Fschemes that could have gone
OL,14,Felsewhere."
OL,16,FHe said "residents have had large
OL,17,Fconstructions outside their homes,
OL,18,Fcrossing the roadway and obstructing
OL,19,Fdaily life."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772644279
OL,3,C#100m cycle lane labelled 'dangerous'
OL,4,Cafter girl, 13, injured on scooter
OL,6,FThe #100 million Transforming Travel
OL,7,FScheme, mainly funded by the
OL,8,Fgovernment with around #10 million
OL,9,Ffrom BCP Council, is expected to cause
OL,10,Ffour years of disruption for residents
OL,11,Fand motorists.
OL,13,FBut BCP Council said the lanes are
OL,14,Fpart of a plan to reduce congestion
OL,15,Fand encourage more cycling.
OL,17,FCouncillor Andy Hadley said: "The
OL,18,Fchallenge is the volume of vehicles in
OL,19,Furban space.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772644279
OL,3,C#100m cycle lane labelled 'dangerous'
OL,4,Cafter girl, 13, injured on scooter
OL,6,F"If a few people change their mode of
OL,7,Ftravel, that creates space for those
OL,8,Fwho absolutely need to use a car."
OL,10,FA stretch of twin cycle lanes on
OL,11,FWillisdown Road in Poole attracted
OL,12,Fnational attention last year for
OL,13,Fseeming underused.
OL,15,FCouncil figures now show an average of
OL,16,F400 cyclists each day, mostly during
OL,17,Frush hour, with numbers expected to
OL,18,Frise to 600 in the summer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772644279
OL,3,C#100m cycle lane labelled 'dangerous'
OL,4,Cafter girl, 13, injured on scooter
OL,6,FBut cyclist Russell Trent, who
OL,7,Fcampaigns for more bike lanes,
OL,8,Fbelieves the new network will make
OL,9,Ftravel safer and easier.
OL,11,F"It's very new.," he said.
OL,13,F"People are resistant to change at
OL,14,Ffirst, but once the networks are
OL,15,Fconnected and properly signposted,
OL,16,Fmore people will start using them," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,FThe lanes have attracted criticism
OL,20,Ffrom Dorset's most senior cycling
OL,21,Fproficiency examiner.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772644279
OL,3,C#100m cycle lane labelled 'dangerous'
OL,4,Cafter girl, 13, injured on scooter
OL,6,FTrevor Shore said even "if a couple of
OL,7,Fbuses stop opposite each other, it
OL,8,Fbrings the whole road to a standstill."
OL,10,FHe added "nobody uses the cycle lanes"
OL,11,Fbecause of its rough surfaces.
OL,13,FThe lane where Laila was injured has
OL,14,Fnow been repaired, and the wider
OL,15,FBournemouth, Christchurch, and Poole
OL,16,Fnetwork is due to be completed this
OL,17,Fsummer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
